cp wp-config-sample.php wp-config.php
nano wp-config.php
Go to MySQL settign and 
                       replace database_name_here with wp_site3
                       replace username_here with with wp_site_user3
                       replace password_here with password
                       replace utf8 with UTF8mb4
                       replace      with utf8mb4_bin
Go to Authentication Unique Keys and Salts
copy the given url and paste in the web browser to get authentication unique keys and salts

Save the file to finish the linking procedure of wordpress to the newly created database
